# Title: Wab Execution From Non Default Location
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-12
# Level: high
# Description: Detects execution of wab.exe (Windows Contacts) and Wabmig.exe (Microsoft Address Book Import Tool) from non default locations as seen with bumblebee activity
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wab_execution_from_non_default_location.yml

Image IN ("*\\wab.exe", "*\\wabmig.exe") NOT (Image IN ("C:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*", "C:\\Program Files\\Windows Mail\\*", "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Windows Mail\\*"))